{"tid":1545383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［非分化］兄弟爬山唔係比政黨政治生存既後門","createTime":"2019-09-06T01:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T01:42:08.000Z","uid":19945,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b05bf4f71b000b33dc51082e6ade36cfdff030ac","tid":1545383,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"譚香文個班仆街<br />\n多年無變口講一齊努力<br />\n扮協調咩反自動當選但又撞幾區<br />\n香港人成個經濟濫炒都唔驚<br />\n會怕你幾個議席<br />\n<br />\n依家講得清清楚楚<br />\n你譚香文班人唔讓返個選位比素人<br />\n同其他先落區既人<br />\n我地寧死都一定一票不投<br />\n<br />\n我成個運動無屌過任何一個泛民<br />\n我絕對唔係分化P牌 道理係我個邊<br />\n共識就係唔撞區 你撞得加埋以前事蹟我絕對唔會相信你係同路人<br />\n三毛要屈隨便你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3e672f62c2c52a78daafb711cca6f6ed416dfe","tid":1545383,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">大個仔</span>獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈<span style=\"font-size: small;\">內容包括</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6379985acc5757f1f9f1fec9aec4706d3cdb031c","tid":1545383,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fceec7e4e3693f55e2287f306d047623df5a9316","tid":1545383,"uid":5031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"推 你要玩野一定同你攬炒<br />\n唔好諗住收割現時風氣同人地既努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b0cbf57e8edc39eb7a7aeca2b2fedc39216c7a","tid":1545383,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:41:12.000Z","msg":"記同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cc7cef2f24a40faa71b078ea65897ab67d6c3a","tid":1545383,"uid":28435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"熱狗又分化叫人唔好投票，勿回 ✋🏻"},{"pid":"ad7c8ab0d334c34406e2b7a0d681dc8bccdf2f4d","tid":1545383,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:42:08.000Z","msg":"Btw譚香文唔係泛民<br />\n佢港大區先迫走親泛民素人"}]}